``` EXAMPLE Splunk SPL — agent tool call outside its allowlist (see .yml).
    Maintain the per-agent allowlist in a lookup (agent_tool_allowlist.csv:
    agent_id, tool_name). Anything not in the lookup is surfaced. ```

index=agent_audit event=tool_call
| lookup agent_tool_allowlist agent_id tool_name OUTPUT tool_name as allowed
| where isnull(allowed)
| stats count values(tool_name) as tools_used min(_time) as first last(_time) as last by agent_id user
| sort - count
